T02D3739:74b-1: a'a rya ga na pa ti r'a ga badzra sa ma ya stod tra na'am /
T02D3739:74b-3: 'phags pa tshogs kyi bdag po chags pa rdo rje'i dam tshig gi bstod pa zhes bya ba /
T02D3739:74b-4: rje btsun spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3739:74b-5: phyag 'tshal dpal ldan tshogs bdag dgyes //
T02D3739:74b-6: phyag 'tshal dpal ldan zhi ba skye //
T02D3739:74b-7: phyag 'tshal dpal ldan khro bo che //
T02D3739:74b-8: tshe 'di nyid la dngos grub ni //
T02D3739:74b-9: ci 'dod par ni stsol bar mdzod //
T02D3739:74b-10: lha yi rgyal po'i mnga' thang ni //
T02D3739:74b-11: sgrub pa po la stsol bar mdzad //
T02D3739:74b-12: shin tu thugs rje'i bdag nyid pas //
T02D3739:74b-13: tshogs bdag chen po thugs rje che //
T02D3739:74b-14: thugs rje chen pos dbul ba skyob //
T02D3739:74b-15: nor lha chen po khyod nyid la //
T02D3739:74b-16: bdag nyid gus pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D3739:74b-17: dpal ldan tshogs bdag chen po ni //
T02D3739:74b-18: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi ba //
T02D3739:75a-2: / la phug ral gri rin chen dang //
T02D3739:75a-3: chang snod la du dgra sta 'dzin //
T02D3739:75a-4: brkyang bskum skyil krung yum steng bzhugs //
T02D3739:75a-5: zhal nang rin chen char pa 'bebs //
T02D3739:75a-6: sgrub pa po yi dbul ba sel //
T02D3739:75a-7: gsus che rgyan rnams kun gyis brgyan //
T02D3739:75a-8: phyag 'tshal dpal ldan tshogs bdag la'o //
T02D3739:75a-9: chang dang la du la phug dang //
T02D3739:75a-10: 'bras chan khur ba'i gtor ma bzhes //
T02D3739:75a-11: tshe dang longs spyod 'phel ba dang //
T02D3739:75a-13: mi dang 'byung po gnod sbyin bdud //
T02D3739:75a-14: thams cad bran du 'gyur par shog / lha yi longs spyod mang po las //
T02D3739:75a-15: 'dod pa'i yon tan 'byung bar shog ; dngos grub sgrub pa'i dbang phyug can //
T02D3739:75a-16: 'dul pa'i dbang gis skur sprul pa //
T02D3739:75a-17: lha chen tshogs bdag chen po ste //
T02D3739:75a-19: byang chub thob pa'i grogs mdzod cig / ces bstod
T02D3739:75a-20: la gsol ba gdang pa ste bzlas pa thon nas
T02D3739:75a-22: / tshogs kyi bdag po chags pa rdo rje dam
T02D3739:75a-23: tshig gi bstod pa pandi ta d'i pam ka ra
T02D3739:75a-24: shr'i dzny'a nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D3739:75a-26: // / pandi ta chen po de nyid dang /
